{"tid":753690,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解以前啲人唔鐘意用eps買野？？到底有咩缺點？","createTime":"2018-07-23T23:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T16:16:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9fed135355ea2a37e5b0c27e6a2fa01e3a37bf95","tid":753690,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T23:23:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_Fd3dVr9_DY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_Fd3dVr9_DY&d=ZEvYQNGYBONbA6mLN9hUzC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a1e1df8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_Fd3dVr9_DY</a>"},{"pid":"88258be510ee019a6a68bf310b2950dd26020ce1","tid":753690,"uid":107269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T23:35:07.000Z","msg":"每個年代都有唔接受新事物既人"},{"pid":"845ad3cb66424fc7008d27cbe43df32c7a3a4261","tid":753690,"uid":32816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T23:36:46.000Z","msg":"要入密碼"},{"pid":"2a39c4da5b918be546b30fa62cf2cbce402a2b4b","tid":753690,"uid":59140,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T23:43:15.000Z","msg":"可能當咗提款咭係信用咭<br />\n因為都係要碌咭<br />\n信用咭要收手續費 EPS唔收"},{"pid":"168ef95eae7162d10951cbc5262aa49d6da95b7f","tid":753690,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T23:45:29.000Z","msg":"用自銀行戶口買野等如開門俾人偷錢"},{"pid":"ade8d53c93ee91c917a1a15aab4ccb46594fdd60","tid":753690,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T23:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能當咗提款咭係信用咭<br />\n因為都係要碌咭<br />\n信用咭要收手續費 EPS唔收</blockquote><br />\n我記得用提款咭經 EPS ,都要收手續費 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係某D商號(如電腦硬件銷售店)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d18bd69312946ebaa13623f502b456e26977a8a","tid":753690,"uid":68457,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T23:56:13.000Z","msg":"原來1985年已經有EPS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係今日角度睇，而家太多付款方式，除左現金、eps，仲有八達通、credit card 更轉左pay wave形式，方便快捷。EPS要輸入密碼浪費商戶+顧客時間。而且EPS即時戶口扣錢，八達通可以完全取代eps嘅功能。credit card 唔單只押後還款期，仲有積分回贈，有著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除非商戶唔支援八達通、credit card (例如診所、部分政府機構)，否則EPS優勢唔大<br />\n<br />\n但唔知商戶角度黎睇有咩影響<br />\n<br />\nbtw，片中睇到以前超市、百貨公司display貨品好多好混亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9175c2817b4cab6a1df7f23f678ef27032c4cf63","tid":753690,"uid":68457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T00:05:38.000Z","msg":"同埋以前啱啱推出credit card，新一代嘅人開始適應credit card消費，又中途整個新嘅EPS咁嘅產物，唔太受落。老一輩又習慣咗多年嘅現金消費模式。"},{"pid":"a7cbaf254cc90b9e1cfb13b8a36128d2453e2213","tid":753690,"uid":59140,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ade8d53c93ee91c917a1a15aab4ccb46594fdd60","tid":753690,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T23:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能當咗提款咭係信用咭<br />\n因為都係要碌咭<br />\n信用咭要收手續費 EPS唔收</blockquote><br />\n我記得用提款咭經 EPS ,都要收手續費 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n特別係某D商號(如電腦硬件銷售店)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T00:08:19.000Z","msg":"嗰啲好似係舖頭自己收錢<br />\n因為EPS係收舖頭手續費，唔係收客手續費"},{"pid":"d41192d5e625241c49ea35215723920cce76dde7","tid":753690,"uid":37489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T00:30:19.000Z","msg":"因為冇優惠囉 而家出個m記十蚊 d人都出曬水咁"},{"pid":"6537c20e016f2de053daf56ac0fc662de8b3ee6d","tid":753690,"uid":43850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T00:45:35.000Z","msg":"金額細既交易正常人銀包都袋錢咪比現金<br />\n金額大既例如買金買珠寶果d 緊係用信用卡有分拎<br />\n正如片中所講 eps推出係為左節省銀行處理現金提存既成本 正常消費者話鳩知你處理一單現金提存既成本係10蚊定1000蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefbeffcf12ef9f0c170c81f6198c64e48ea1e4b","tid":753690,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":